            <h3>Benefits of Vehicle Loans</h3>
            <p>Vehicle loans offer several advantages for those looking to purchase a vehicle:</p>
            <p><b>Affordability:</b> They allow you to spread the cost of the vehicle over several years, making it more affordable in the short term.</p>
            <p><b>Ownership:</b> You get to own the vehicle and can use it as you see fit.</p>
            <p><b>Credit Building:</b> Timely loan payments can help improve your credit score.</p>
            <p><b>Convenience:</b> Many lenders offer online loan applications and convenient payment options.</p>
